PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of William Keays, of Sainte-Foy, Quebec, as a director of the board of directors of the Port of Quebec Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Denise Rancourt Bélanger, whose term has expired.

precis:
Approval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of William Keays,
of Sainte-Foy, Quebec, as a director of the board of directors of the Port
of Quebec Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three
years, in the place of Denise Rancourt Bélanger, whose term has expired.
